short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: brings the power and elegance of luxury supercars to your browser's new tab experience.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Each background captures a different supercar set against a stunning cityscape at dusk or night, combining the sleek design of the car with the allure of the city's lights. Whether you're a car enthusiast or simply appreciate the beauty of automotive excellence, this extension will provide you with an immersive and stylish browsing atmosphere.
